ʻO Barack Obama hānau ʻia ma ʻAukake 4, 1961) ka pelekikena o ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻia i kēia manawa. ʻO ia ka pelekikena kanahākūmāhā, a ʻo ia ka pelekikena ʻApelika-ʻAmelika hoʻokahi.
ʻO Donald H. Keefer hānau ʻia ma August 18, 1916) is an actor from ʻAmelika Hui Pū ʻia.
